[ti:Midnight Rain (WortRadar-Demo)]
[ar:Eigenkomposition - frei verwendbar]
[00:12.40] Midnight rain keeps falling on the windowpane
[00:16.10] I'm chasing shadows through a labyrinth of doubt
[00:20.55] Your whispered promises evaporate like haze
[00:24.80] We were reckless, we were furtive, sneaking out
[00:29.00] Every heartbeat is a drum inside my chest
[00:33.30] The serendipity of meeting you that night
[00:37.60] Now the embers of our love refuse to rest
[00:41.90] And I'm dancing with your ghost until the light
[00:46.20] Oh, the gutters overflow, the streetlights flicker
[00:50.50] My resolve is getting thinner, getting weak
[00:54.80] Every memory of you returns much quicker
[00:59.10] Than the courage that I need before I speak
[01:03.40] Midnight rain, wash away the words I never said
[01:07.70] Midnight rain, drown the echoes in my head
